            <title>[CASSANDRA-10228] JVMStabilityInspector should inspect cause and suppressed exceptions</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-10228</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;JVMStabilityInspector only checks the outer exception, but this can wrap or otherwise suppress an exception we do consider &quot;unstable&quot;. We should check all of the exceptions in an exception graph before deciding things are kosher.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
